Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:09.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:12.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:16.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:24.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:34.75,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.77,0:00:41.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:48.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:56.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:03.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:10.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.48,0:01:14.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:21.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:25.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:29.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:32.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:41.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:49.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.06,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.57,0:01:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Luffy get cut down by Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.49,0:02:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.62,0:02:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's our captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn swordsman...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna harm the ladies,\NI'll be your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "I still haven't\Nplayed my trump card yet"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:56.28,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Last Counterattack by the Memory\NThief Who Revealed His True Colors!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oooh! All right! I'm... me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! I'm me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but aren't you one of the guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I'm a guest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I dressed like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, manager?!\NPlease come to the front desk right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right... I'm the inn manager, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mom! Where have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. Are you okay? How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:04:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Our memories...\NOur memories are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everyone! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's you, Drim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.45,0:04:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare us like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drim... Drim...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like everyone's memories are back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.97,0:04:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did something like that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.98,0:04:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who took our\Nmemories away is in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.30,0:05:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"T-Take them out, Roronoa Zoro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-See? He's being controlled by that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, someone, do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... You damn swordsman,\Nyou're always bringing in trouble...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, Sanji! Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.55,0:05:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Now this will buy me some time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:06:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Collier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you idiot cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.77,0:06:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! What'd you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro, did you just... say "Luffy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:06:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your memories are back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is scary! If your memories are back,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then approach us with\Na smiling, kind face like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Who am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--Hey! Don't make it more\Ncomplicated than it already is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Zoro! How dare you do that earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.18,0:07:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, do what you want, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Now we're all back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-chan really is wonderful, to figure out\Nthat that sea horse horn is the real culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! So that was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the first one to\Nget your memories back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you notice it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! I'm better than Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So where did that thing go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:08:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's so obvious where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. It turned pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should've hurried up and escaped.\NDoes it think it's hiding wel--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! How dare you manipulate me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna catch and fillet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, his feelings are hurt in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Now, catch me if you can!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.88,0:08:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You really piss me off! Hold it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Hahaha! You can't catch me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Then how about this?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm right here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What?! No way! Now, I'm getting serious!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.35,0:08:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"There, I've caught you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:09:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not gonna let you go!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're next, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm going to play my... trump card"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.22,0:09:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san... is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaya...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you better now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoooa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...afterimages of their memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna fight, you jerks?!\NI'll kick all your asses at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Thanks to you guys, I even lost all the\Nmemories I collected from the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I can obtain all your rich memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can become one!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.14,0:11:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not going to miss this opportunity!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.06,0:12:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:13:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the one who's drowning over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.03,0:13:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"All right! I was able to\Nbecome a Millennial Dragon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You...!\N--Amazing! You can understand what it's saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Err...\N--Hey... This raccoon dog talks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Am I a raccoon dog?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A talking raccoon dog and a Millennial Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a damn bastard who almost drowned...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watching that dragon...\Nsomehow gets me pissed off! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? How? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange... Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.99,0:13:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon, huh? I wanna ride it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot? There's no\Nway you can ride it from...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know until you try... Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! My arms and legs stretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really jumped on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... What's with his body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous! Hey, keep still!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow that thing looks like it's in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let go of me! Hey! The memories\Nare going to leak out"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:15:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.49,0:15:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you steal our memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it saying?! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper? M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could it be?! Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I was finally able to become a\NMillennial Dragon! Don't interfere!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People's memories aren't yours to take!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna become a Millennial Dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,become one by making your own big memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shut up! Take this! This is it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum... Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna fly that bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.14,0:17:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kicked its ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I remember right,\Ndon't Millennial Dragons hatch from eggs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.83,0:17:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You can't become one\Njust by eating memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you probably don't know it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we saw it with our own eyes\Nbefore we entered the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, forget that. People must be\Nmaking a racket in the village by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're their benefactors who\Ngot all the villagers' memories back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt they're gonna treat us like heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First all-you-can-drink party\Nwe've had in a while, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.48,0:17:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something you wanna forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.77,0:17:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like we can expect\Nthem to reward us good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a bronze statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.11,0:18:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be so popular\Nwith girls, huh? Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Robin? If you're able\Nto get something, what would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Books, as expected?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. If possible, maybe books\Non this island's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! I want a medical book--\None that's this thick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can see the seashore now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.85,0:18:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, ladies and gentlemen!\NThanks for coming to greet us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.06,0:18:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um... H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.53,0:18:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Aren't we supposed to be heroes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me! I wanna ask that question myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Where's the waver?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.38,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! Stop right there, pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn memory thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn girl! Pay your bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.51,0:19:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with them?! They think we did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.60,0:19:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're pirates. It can't be helped, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that it's come to this,\Nwe're to the point of desperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What pirate would stop just\Nbecause they're told to stop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we made it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A big bronze statue... It was so close...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:20:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to being built... A big, dark statue...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that losing memories\Nwould turn into such a big fuss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I totally agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was even some guy who\Nschemed to make us his pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.03,0:20:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Sanji-kun... I just got\Ncarried away... I just got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there was a damn simpleton\Nwhose body and soul got taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.84,0:20:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, if you were\Nactually standing guard,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this racket wouldn't have happened,\Nyou idiot moss-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I was sleepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna sleep that much,\Nsleep for the rest of your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! Shut up! That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.52,0:20:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or would you like to lose your memories again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Nami-san! Please don't say things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:21:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't gotten my memories back...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what would I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong... Robin?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little sleepy, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just natural. Robin-chan hasn't\Nslept much because of this racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, that's right!\N--All right then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make a special healthy dinner with\Na mixture of herbal medicines tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, food! I forgot about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make it now, so just wait quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say, Luffy.\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you come back\Nwith Zoro at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Well, I got stuck\Nunder a rock Zoro cut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A rock?!\N--Yeah. That was one huge, hard rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.98,0:22:09.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.11,0:22:12.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.65,0:22:18.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.24,0:22:20.52,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.54,0:22:23.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:29.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:35.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:37.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:40.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.89,0:22:43.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:46.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:52.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.19,0:22:55.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.07,0:22:57.80,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:23:00.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.41,0:23:08.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, things have been settled.\NTo the next island, full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.09,0:23:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're full of hot air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think with this incident, you've all\Nlearned how important memories are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.10,0:23:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to summarize for?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.43,0:23:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? I feel like I just saw something\NI don't wanna remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that Split-Head is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.60,0:23:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.98,0:23:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.27,0:23:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Proud Man! Silver Fox Foxy"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Him again?
